t book I'll read this year. The characters, Ivoree, Peter, Henry.....they are just so real and they all just touched a place in my heart that fictional characters rarely reach. This story of an \"old maid\" (30 years old!) whose life becomes entangled with an almost feral 8 year old boy is wonderful to behold, the love that's there, the sacrifice, the compassion. Ivoree is so brutally honest and straight-forward, speaks straight from the heart. I listened to this book on audio and it was narrated by the author, and she did a fantastic job. She tells the entire story in a back-hills of Tennessee southern drawl that is perfect. I believe in this case the audio is probably better than reading it on the printed page. Listen to this book, you will not be sorry.","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/3252519?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/494992264"},"likeCount":6,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":1,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.db-A7vJWinCaorcBUhuqpw":{"id":"kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.db-A7vJWinCaorcBUhuqpw","__typename":"Contributor","works":{"__typename":"ContributorWorksConnection","totalCount":2}},"User:3749999":{"id":3749999,"__typename":"User","legacyId":3749999,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1442529888i/3749999._UX200_CR0,50,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":true,"textReviewsCount":108,"viewableName":"Vera Marie","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/3749999-vera-marie","contributor":{"__ref":"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.db-A7vJWinCaorcBUhuqpw"},"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":12},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.TAicOXlZIoAbhzl3uRUiTQ":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.TAicO